data.description: Welcome home! No HOA!! Spacious and charming, this two-story; 2 car garage, 3 sided brick home sits in a quiet community and has a customized above ground pool with a deck. The Entry Foyer is next to a home office and a large dining room right next to the open kitchen which includes, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and more. The open Breakfast area leads to a grand family room that has tray-high ceilings with tons of natural light throughout the home. In-law suite on the main floor with Full Bath. Upstairs, you will find the Owners Suite with a separate private room that can be an office, Gym, Study room or meditation room, the bathroom has his and hers closets, and three large bedrooms upstairs. Enjoy time with family and friends in your own personalized MAN CAVE Bar and Movie Room or Step outside tot he pool to spend time with family and friends. Near food shops and entertainment..A must see..
